metadata.name: LPEPE - Candy Shop
metadata.description:
Pepe isn't just a frog; Pepe is a lifestyle!
Life is more beautiful with pepes and lollypops!!🐸🍭


Light painting refers to a technique of image creation using light directly and recording that by taking a long exposure photograph with Bulb photography, without any special tools or brushes, just a small lamp and hand movement.
All Details of this work, including design, light painting, Photography, Motion and also the music were created by lollypop!🍭
